<id>http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=4769&amp;p=42257#p42257</id>
<link href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=4769&amp;p=42257#p42257"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[LDH syntax inconvenience, improvements?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=4769&amp;p=42257#p42257"><![CDATA[
And on the 65816:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">pea $1234<br />pld        ; direct page = $1234, rather than the default of $0000<br />lda $34    ; accesses $0034 if assembled to AD 34 00, $1268 if assembled to A5 34</div><br />And on the SPC-700:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">setp       ; direct page = $100<br />mov a,$34  ; accesses $0034 if assembled to E5 34 00, $0134 if assembled to E4 34</div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=17">blargg</a> — Fri Jan 23, 2009 7:01 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
